{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2854474b2e","title":"国民党提出的谈判条件","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"759254e037","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":17,"articleId":"2854474b2e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"75fb3e25fe","type":"paragraph","text":"国民党提出的谈判条件！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"566d0fddc1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月17日）朱、张，徐、陈，任、贺、关、刘，并告彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"cad208aacb","type":"paragraph","text":"（中）与南京谈判有急转直下势，第三次与南京联络之代表十四回西安，携带来国民党条件如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"ceafd48263","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）苏维埃区域可以存在（二）红军名义不要改联军，待遇与国军同。（三）共产党代表公开参加国民大会。（四）即派人具体谈判。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"4cd6e8a3c4","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）蒋介石十六日到西安，我们正交涉由蒋派飞机到肤施接恩来到西安与蒋直接谈判","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"9f50a86ef5","type":"paragraph","text":"（内）为根本停止胡宗南进攻或延缓其进攻期，请你们速将十五日泽东谈话大批印刷，多数小支队直接送各国民党军队，主要是胡宗南、朱绍良，另由向前写信给胡，内附泽东谈话，派专人由静宁送胡（静宁已由胡部接防）。如何，盼即复","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"39671d9d17","type":"paragraph","text":"洛泽周","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"f4c08ea7d9","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日十六时","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"},{"id":"9d57f6b4da","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和洛甫（张闻天）、周恩来给朱德、张国森、徐向前、陈昌浩、任时、贺龙、关向应、刘伯承并告彭德怀的电报。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e"}],"page":{"id":"66ba86b281","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"2854474b2e","start":234,"end":234}}}},"__N_SSG":true}